==English==
===Etymology===
From the [[w:Middle_Latin_language|ML]], from [[w:Latin_language|Latin]] for ''[[fishpond]],'' from ''[[piscis]].'' (1793)

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A drained [[basin]] near a church's [[altar]] for the [[disposal]] of water from [[liturgical]] [[ablutions]].

